        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://houston.craigslist.org/sec/6044179781.html"></div>
        </div>
<b><font size="5">Top Gun Security &amp;  Investigations</b> is seeking security professionals for full time and part time positions <b>in Houston and surrounding areas!</b></font>
<ul><font color="navy">
<li>Noncommissioned (unarmed) officers needed!</li>
<li>Commissioned (armed) officers needed!</li></font>
<li><font color="green"><b>Are you new to security?</b> No prior experience is necessary! With a minimum of 6 hours of state certified training and minimal training cost, you can take your first step toward a broad new career! <b>Apply today for further details!</b></font></li> &#65279;
</ul>
<b>Qualifications for candidacy:</b>
<ul>
<li>You must have a clean criminal background</li>
<li> Be at least 18 years of age</li>
<li>You must have a valid Texas Driver's License or Texas ID and Social Security Card</li>
<li> Professional appearance and demeanor</li>
<li> Attention to detail and surroundings</li>
<li> Must be in reasonable physical condition to perform job duties independently</li>
<li> Active cell phone and email</li>
<li> Reliable personal transportation</li>
<li> You must be drug free</li>
</ul>
Top Gun Security &amp; Investigations (License # C-17683) is among the strongest security companies in the business, providing state of the art equipment, technology, and training. From our Academy to our professional appearance, we are certain you will agree that Top Gun is second to none in the security profession. If you have the drive and determination to be a true security professional, you owe it to yourself to join our team! Why build your career with Top Gun? Top Gun's core ideology is much more than a simple idea in practice. It continues to evolve as it breaks boundaries.
<br>
<br>
<b>Why build a career with Top Gun?</b>
<ul>
<li>The fastest growth of any security company in Texas among 4 major cities</li>
<li>Fast advancement opportunities</li>
<li>Discounted training upgrades exclusively for Top Gun employees</li>
<li>On-call, holiday, and overtime pay</li>
<li>Officer support network</li>
<li>IRA &amp; Roth IRA programs</li>
<li>Vacation time after 1 year of service with additional time after 2 years of service</li>
<li>Guaranteed Annual raise every year</li>
<li>Internal Promotions that pay more income/bonuses</li>
<li>Officer of the Month with bonuses and company wide recognition</li>
<li>Officer Relief Fund that assists with Officer emergencies and/or their families</li> 
<li>Company-wide Bible upon request program and annual Bible drive for officers and their families</li>
<li>Company Chaplain along with a prayer request via company-wide email</li>
<li>Personable, organized administrative staff</li>
<li>Recognition</li>
<li>Lateral transfers to/from other branches</li>
<li>Exceptional teaching staff comprised of in-house police officers and military veterans</li>
</ul>
<b><font size="5">Reply today to begin your new security career with Top Gun!</b></font>
<p><b><font size="4"><font color="navy"><a href="http://www.topgun-securityservices.com" rel="nofollow">Visit the Top Gun Website!</a></b></font></p></font>    </section>

